            {
              "id": "ac44eb8",
              "elType": "widget",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>In response to this environmental degradation, Yantze Farm embarked on a transformative journey. This journey was not without risks—seedlings, earthworks, and plant nurseries are fragile in their early stages. However, the Vetiver System emerged as an invaluable ally, ensuring that the implementation of regenerative practices was resilient and effective.</p><p>Vetiver grass, with its deep-rooted strength, became the guardian of this transformation. As a steadfast companion, it helped replace the monoculture with a thriving, biodiverse ecosystem. In less than two years, the farm’s vision of reforestation, spearheaded by the rapid growth of bamboo, transformed the landscape.</p>",
                "align": "justify",
                "_margin": {
