                      "elType": "widget",
                      "settings": {
                        "editor": "<p>The success of Vetiver and the broader regenerative movement depends on awareness. As more people learn about the possibilities Vetiver offers, its adoption will spread, leading to more sustainable practices worldwide. The partnership between VSF and Gaia Verso embodies the ripple effect that occurs when like-minded organizations unite for a common cause.</p><p>As VSF and Gaia Verso continue to collaborate, we look forward to exciting developments in the world of Vetiver and regenerative practices. Together, they are not only planting the seeds of change but nurturing a vision of a greener, more sustainable future for all.</p>",
